 radius and pill-shaped buttons (24px radius)\n181\t- Lavender primary (#7C3AED) with Blush Rose secondary (#F9A8D4) accents\n182\t- Bottom navigation with 4 tabs and active state indicator pills\n183\t- SVG-based inline icons throughout\n184\t- Nunito font family with generous line-height for calm readability\n185\t- Gentle spring-based animations (200-300ms ease-out transitions)\n186\t\n187\t## Implementation Notes\n188\t\n189\t- All screens use the 4-tab bottom navigation shell\n190\t- Push routes hide the bottom navigation bar\n191\t- Full-sheet overlays cover the entire screen (used for breathing exercise animation)\n192\t- Bottom-sheet overlays slide up from the bottom edge for contextual forms\n193\t- FAB appears on push routes that support entry creation (cycle-tracking, weight-nutrition, health-log)"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"646ef3a5-9221-4d37-8f83-7525abe1aec0","uuid":"db41ea5b-7804-49ea-9aa3-da9048ebd829","timestamp":"2026-05-18T23:44:35.174Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/minh/Documents/openplayboosks/examples/baby-app/.stitch/system/META.md","content":"# Pregnant Tracker - Baby Bump — Design Reference (META)\n\n## Overview\n\nThis document serves as a machine-readable index and cross-reference for the design system. It maps design decisions to their source of truth, lists available assets, and provides tooling metadata.\n\n---\n\n## Design System Identity\n\n| Field | Value |\n|---|---|\n| Theme name | Gentle Bloom |\n| Primary mode | Light |\n| Version | 1.0 |\n| Created | 2026-05-18 |\n\n---\n\n## Source Files\n\n| File | Purpose |\n|---|---|\n| `.stitch/UX.md` | UX specification with vibe, user personas, screens, navigation |\n| `.stitch/screens.json` | Screen definitions with IDs, routes, and feature lists |\n| `.stitch/system/DESIGN.md` | Design system specification with colors, typography, components |\n\n---\n\n## Font Stack\n\n| Role | Font | Weights | Source |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| Display + Body 