[2026-05-18T23:44:38.665Z] [STDOUT] {"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"call_function_8j8lc0popyij_1","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t# Flutter HTML Glossary — `data-flutter` Attributes\n2\t\n3\tMinimal set of `data-flutter` hints for Flutter-specific widgets that have no HTML/Tailwind equivalent. **ALL styling is done via Tailwind classes** — these attributes only tell the converter which Flutter widget to use.\n4\t\n5\t## Why Two Systems?\n6\t\n7\t- **Tailwind classes** → styling (colors, spacing, typography, borders, shadows, layout)\n8\t- **`data-flutter` attributes** → widget identity (Scaffold, AppBar, Hero, CachedImage, etc.)\n9\t\n10\tAI writes beautiful Tailwind naturally. `data-flutter` adds the minimal Flutter-specific context needed for accurate conversion.\n11\t\n12\t---\n13\t\n14\t## Scaffold & App Chrome\n15\t\n16\t```html\n17\t<!-- Scaffold — the root of every screen -->\n18\t<div data-flutter=\"scaffold\" class=\"flex flex-col min-h-screen bg-slate-950\">\n19\t\n20\t  <!-- AppBar -->\n21\t  <header data-flutter=\"app-bar\" class=\"flex items-center h-14 px-4 bg-slate-900\">\n22\t    <button aria-label=\"Back\" class=\"w-10 h-10 ...\"><svg><!-- arrow_back --></svg></button>\n23\t    <h1 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-white\">Title</h1>\n24\t  </header>\n25\t\n26\t  <!-- Body — main scrollable content -->\n27\t  <main class=\"flex-1 overflow-y-auto\">\n28\t    <!-- content -->\n29\t  </main>\n30\t\n31\t  <!-- Bottom Navigation -->\n32\t  <nav data-flutter=\"bottom-nav\" class=\"flex justify-around h-14 bg-slate-900 border-t border-slate-800\">\n33\t    <button data-flutter=\"nav-destination\" data-icon=\"home\" data-label=\"Home\" data-selected=\"true\"\n34\t            class=\"flex flex-col items-center gap-0.5 text-amber-500\">\n35\t      <svg><!-- home icon --></svg>\n36\t      <span class=\"text-xs\">Home</span>\n37\t    </button>\n38\t    <button data-flutter=\"nav-destination\" data-icon=\"search\" data-label=\"Browse\"\n39\t            class=\"flex flex-col items-center gap-0.5 text-slate-500\">\n40\t      <svg><!-- search icon --></svg>\n41\t      <span class=\"text-xs\">Browse</span>\n42\t    </button>\n43\t  </nav>\n44\t\n45\t  <!-- FAB -->\n46\t  <button data-flutter=\"fab\" data-icon=\"add\" class=\"absolute bottom-20 right-4 w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-amber-500 shadow-lg\">\n47\t    <svg><!-- add icon --></svg>\n48\t  </button>\n49\t</div>\n50\t```\n51\t\n52\t## Scrolling & Slivers\n53\t\n54\t```html\n55\t<!-- CustomScrollView with SliverAppBar -->\n56\t<div data-flutter=\"custom-scroll\" class=\"flex-1\">\n57\t  <header data-flutter=\"sliver-app-bar\" data-expanded-height=\"200\" data-pinned=\"true\"\n58\t          class=\"bg-slate-900\">\n59\t    <img class=\"w-full h-full object-cover\" src=\"...\" />\n60\t    <h1 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-white\">Title</h1>\n61\t  </header>\n62\t  <div data-flutter=\"sliver-list\">\n63\t    <!-- list items -->\n64\t  </div>\n65\t</div>\n66\t\n67\t<!-- Pull to refresh -->\n68\t<div data-flutter=\"refresh\" class=\"flex-1\">\n69\t  <!-- scrollable content -->\n70\t</div>\n71\t\n72\t<!-- Safe area -->\n73\t<div data-flutter=\"safe-area\">\n74\t  <!-- content -->\n75\t</div>\n76\t```\n77\t\n78\t## Tabs\n79\t\n80\t```html\n81\t<div data-flutter=\"tab-bar\" class=\"flex bg-slate-900 border-b border-slate-800\">\n82\t  <button class=\"flex-1 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-amber-500 border-b-2 border-amber-500\">Reading</button>\n83\t  <button class=\"flex-1 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-slate-500\">Completed</button>\n84\t</div>\n85\t<div data-flutter=\"tab-view\" class=\"flex-1\">\n86\t  <!-- tab panels -->\n87\t</div>\n88\t```\n89\t\n90\t## Hero Animations\n91\t\n92\t```html\n93\t<div data-flutter=\"hero\" data-tag=\"novel-cover-1\">\n94\t  <img class=\"w-20 h-28 rounded-lg object-cover\" src=\"...\" />\n95\t</div>\n96\t```\n97\t\n98\t## Images\n99\t\n100\t```html\n101\t<!-- CachedNetworkImage -->\n102\t<img data-flutter=\"cached-image\" class=\"w-20 h-28 rounded-lg object-cover\" src=\"...\" />\n103\t\n104\t<!-- Regular image (no data-flutter needed) -->\n105\t<img class=\"w-full h-48 object-cover\" src=\"...\" />\n106\t```\n107\t\n108\t## Overlays\n109\t\n110\t```html\n111\t<div data-flutter=\"bottom-sheet\" class=\"bg-slate-900 rounded-t-2xl p-4\">\n112\t  <!-- sheet content -->\n113\t</div>\n114\t\n115\t<div data-flutter=\"dialog\" class=\"bg-slate-900 rounded-2xl p-6 max-w-sm\">\n116\t  <h2 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-white\">Confirm</h2>\n117\t  <p class=\"text-sm text-slate-400 mt-2\">Are you sure?</p>\n118\t</div>\n119\t```\n120\t\n121\t---\n122\t\n123\t## Complete `data-flutter` Reference\n124\t\n125\t| Value | Flutter Widget | Extra Attributes |\n126\t|-------|---------------|------------------|\n127\t| `scaffold` | `Scaffold()` | — |\n128\t| `app-bar` | `AppBar()` | — |\n129\t| `bottom-nav` | `NavigationBar()` | — |\n130\t| `nav-destination` | `NavigationDestination()` | `data-icon`, `data-label`, `data-selected` |\n131\t| `fab` | `FloatingActionButton()` | `data-icon` |\n132\t| `hero` | `Hero()` | `data-tag` |\n133\t| `cached-image` | `CachedNetworkImage()` | — |\n134\t| `sliver-app-bar` | `SliverAppBar()` | `data-expanded-height`, `data-pinned` |\n135\t| `custom-scroll` | `CustomScrollView()` | — |\n136\t| `sliver-list` | `SliverList()` | — |\n137\t| `sliver-grid` | `SliverGrid()` | `data-columns` |\n138\t| `tab-bar` | `TabBar()` | — |\n139\t| `tab-view` | `TabBarView()` | — |\n140\t| `bottom-sheet` | `showModalBottomSheet()` | — |\n141\t| `dialog` | `showDialog()` / `AlertDialog` | — |\n142\t| `safe-area` | `SafeArea()` | — |\n143\t| `refresh` | `RefreshIndicator()` | — |\n144\t\n145\t---\n146\t\n147\t## Rules\n148\t\n149\t1. **Tailwind does ALL styling** — colors, spacing, typography, borders, shadows, layout\n150\t2. **`data-flutter` only for identity** — which Flutter widget, not how it looks\n151\t3. **`data-flutter` is optional** — most elements inferred from HTML + Tailwind (`div.flex.flex-col` → Column)\n152\t4. **Icons** — inline SVG with comment: `<!-- home -->`, `<!-- arrow_back -->`\n153\t5. **Converter reads** Tailwind classes + `data-flutter` + HTML structure — CSS is ignored\n154\t"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"646ef3a5-9221-4d37-8f83-7525abe1aec0","uuid":"4cbe334e-8abf-4d6d-a12c-1e7479e6362f","timestamp":"2026-05-18T23:44:38.665Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/minh/Documents/openplayboosks/examples/baby-app/.converge/skills/stitch-flutter/references/flutter-html-glossary.md","content":"# Flutter HTML Glossary — `data-flutter` Attributes\n\nMinimal set of `data-flutter` hints for Flutter-specific widgets that have no HTML/Tailwind equivalent. **ALL styling is done via Tailwind classes** — these attributes only tell the converter which Flutter widget to use.\n\n## Why Two Systems?\n\n- **Tailwind classes** → styling (colors, spacing, typography, borders, shadows, layout)\n- **`data-flutter` attributes** → widget identity (Scaffold, AppBar, Hero, CachedImage, etc.)\n\nAI writes beautiful Tailwind naturally. `data-flutter` adds the minimal Flutter-specific context needed for accurate conversion.\n\n---\n\n## Scaffold & App Chrome\n\n```html\n<!-- Scaffold — the root of every screen -->\n<div data-flutter=\"scaffold\" class=\"flex flex-col min-h-screen bg-slate-950\">\n\n  <!-- AppBar -->\n  <header data-flutter=\"app-bar\" class=\"flex items-center h-14 px-4 bg-slate-900\">\n    <button aria-label=\"Back\" class=\"w-10 h-10 ...\"><svg><!-- arrow_back --></svg></button>\n    <h1 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-white\">Title</h1>\n  </header>\n\n  <!-- Body — main scrollable content -->\n  <main class=\"flex-1 overflow-y-auto\">\n    <!-- content -->\n  </main>\n\n  <!-- Bottom Navigation -->\n  <nav data-flutter=\"bottom-nav\" class=\"flex justify-around h-14 bg-slate-900 border-t border-slate-800\">\n    <button data-flutter=\"nav-destination\" data-icon=\"home\" data-label=\"Home\" data-selected=\"true\"\n            class=\"flex flex-col items-center gap-0.5 text-amber-500\">\n      <svg><!-- home icon --></svg>\n      <span class=\"text-xs\">Home</span>\n    </button>\n    <button data-flutter=\"nav-destination\" data-icon=\"search\" data-label=\"Browse\"\n            class=\"flex flex-col items-center gap-0.5 text-slate-500\">\n      <svg><!-- search icon --></svg>\n      <span class=\"text-xs\">Browse</span>\n    </button>\n  </nav>\n\n  <!-- FAB -->\n  <button data-flutter=\"fab\" data-icon=\"add\" class=\"absolute bottom-20 right-4 w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-amber-500 shadow-lg\">\n    <svg><!-- add icon --></svg>\n  </button>\n</div>\n```\n\n## Scrolling & Slivers\n\n```html\n<!-- CustomScrollView with SliverAppBar -->\n<div data-flutter=\"custom-scroll\" class=\"flex-1\">\n  <header data-flutter=\"sliver-app-bar\" data-expanded-height=\"200\" data-pinned=\"true\"\n          class=\"bg-slate-900\">\n    <img class=\"w-full h-full object-cover\" src=\"...\" />\n    <h1 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-white\">Title</h1>\n  </header>\n  <div data-flutter=\"sliver-list\">\n    <!-- list items -->\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<!-- Pull to refresh -->\n<div data-flutter=\"refresh\" class=\"flex-1\">\n  <!-- scrollable content -->\n</div>\n\n<!-- Safe area -->\n<div data-flutter=\"safe-area\">\n  <!-- content -->\n</div>\n```\n\n## Tabs\n\n```html\n<div data-flutter=\"tab-bar\" class=\"flex bg-slate-900 border-b border-slate-800\">\n  <button class=\"flex-1 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-amber-500 border-b-2 border-amber-500\">Reading</button>\n  <button class=\"flex-1 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-slate-500\">Completed</button>\n</div>\n<div data-flutter=\"tab-view\" class=\"flex-1\">\n  <!-- tab panels -->\n</div>\n```\n\n## Hero Animations\n\n```html\n<div data-flutter=\"hero\" data-tag=\"novel-cover-1\">\n  <img class=\"w-20 h-28 rounded-lg object-cover\" src=\"...\" />\n</div>\n```\n\n## Images\n\n```html\n<!-- CachedNetworkImage -->\n<img data-flutter=\"cached-image\" class=\"w-20 h-28 rounded-lg object-cover\" src=\"...\" />\n\n<!-- Regular image (no data-flutter needed) -->\n<img class=\"w-full h-48 object-cover\" src=\"...\" />\n```\n\n## Overlays\n\n```html\n<div data-flutter=\"bottom-sheet\" class=\"bg-slate-900 rounded-t-2xl p-4\">\n  <!-- sheet content -->\n</div>\n\n<div data-flutter=\"dialog\" class=\"bg-slate-900 rounded-2xl p-6 max-w-sm\">\n  <h2 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-white\">Confirm</h2>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-slate-400 mt-2\">Are you sure?</p>\n</div>\n```\n\n---\n\n## Complete `data-flutter` Reference\n\n| Value | Flutter Widget | Extra Attributes |\n|-------|---------------|------------------|\n| `scaffold` | `Scaffold()` | — |\n| `app-bar` | `AppBar()` | — |\n| `bottom-nav` | `NavigationBar()` | — |\n| `nav-destination` | `NavigationDestination()` | `data-icon`, `data-label`, `data-selected` |\n| `fab` | `FloatingActionButton()` | `data-icon` |\n| `hero` | `Hero()` | `data-tag` |\n| `cached-image` | `CachedNetworkImage()` | — |\n| `sliver-app-bar` | `SliverAppBar()` | `data-expanded-height`, `data-pinned` |\n| `custom-scroll` | `CustomScrollView()` | — |\n| `sliver-list` | `SliverList()` | — |\n| `sliver-grid` | `SliverGrid()` | `data-columns` |\n| `tab-bar` | `TabBar()` | — |\n| `tab-view` | `TabBarView()` | — |\n| `bottom-sheet` | `showModalBottomSheet()` | — |\n| `dialog` | `showDialog()` / `AlertDialog` | — |\n| `safe-area` | `SafeArea()` | — |\n| `refresh` | `RefreshIndicator()` | — |\n\n---\n\n## Rules\n\n1. **Tailwind does ALL styling** — colors, spacing, typography, borders, shadows, layout\n2. **`data-flutter` only for identity** — which Flutter widget, not how it looks\n3. **`data-flutter` is optional** — most elements inferred from HTML + Tailwind (`div.flex.flex-col` → Column)\n4. **Icons** — inline SVG with comment: `<!-- home -->`, `<!-- arrow_back -->`\n5. **Converter reads** Tailwind classes + `data-flutter` + HTML structure — CSS is ignored\n","numLines":154,"startLine":1,"totalLines":154}}}
